# Robot Rumble

Start dev:
```
docker-compose -f docker-compose.dev.yml up
```

Start prod:
```
docker-compose -d -f docker-compose.prod.yml up
```

Run a mix command:
```
docker-compose exec app mix [COMMAND]
```

Remote-shell into the Phoenix process:
```
docker ps # find the id of the app container
docker-compose exec app iex --sname local --cookie abc --remsh "robot@[ID]"
```
